==English==
===Verb===
'''to becue'''  (''transitive'' and ''intransitive'')
#(''nautical'') To [[make fast]] a [[rope]] to an [[anchor]] when on [[rocky]] [[ground]]; the rope is made fast to the [[fluke]]s and [[lightly]] [[tied]] to the [[ring]] - if the flukes are caught on the rocks, a sharp [[jerk]] will [[break]] the tie to the ring, and the anchor can be [[hoisted]], [[upside down]], from the flukes.